# Approval Logic

## Objective
Enforce the peer-review gate logically.

## Tasks
1. Update RLS policies or database mutation functions handling quest status updates.
2. Reject updates to "Done" status unless the request includes a valid approval signature or is performed by a valid peer reviewer.
3. Validate that the user approving the quest is NOT the same user that executed it.
